# atlas.millennium.n6 — 밀레니엄 7대 난제 전용 아틀라스
#
# SSOT: $NEXUS/shared/n6/atlas.millennium.n6
# 생성: 2026-04-16
# 근거: atlas.signals.n6 (94 밀레니엄 signal), DFS 26차 348 tight
# 목적: 7대 난제별 n=6 구조 관찰의 계층적 정리
# 정직: 7대 난제 해결 = 0/7. tight ≠ proof.
#
# 문법:
#   @MS {id} = {statement} :: millennium [{problem}] [{grade}]
#   문제 태그: [7R] Riemann [7P] P-vs-NP [7Y] Yang-Mills
#             [7N] Navier-Stokes [7H] Hodge [7B] BSD [7C] Poincaré
#   등급: [M10*] EXACT검증 [M10] EXACT [M9] NEAR
#         [M7!] breakthrough후보 [M7] EMPIRICAL [M5] 약신호
#         [M?] 가설 [MN] NULL
#   증거: [EP] 증명 [E3] 3중독립 [E2] 2중 [E1] 단일 [EC] cross [EF] formal
#
# 참조:
#   spec: n6shared/specs/atlas.signals.n6.spec.v0.3-draft.md
#   signal SSOT: $NEXUS/shared/n6/atlas.signals.n6
#   DFS 현황: reports/millennium-dfs-status.md (v3)
#   closure: theory/breakthroughs/millennium-7-closure-2026-04-11.md
