# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# §1. 리만 가설 (RH) — BT-541
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#   도메인 EXACT: 20/20 | DFS tight: ~48 | 해결: X
#   핵심: Bilateral Theorem B (k=n=6 Bernoulli 경계)
#   signal: SIG-7R-001~002, 201~210, 401, 501~504

@MS RH-CORE-01 = Theorem B: min{k : numer(B_2k) ≥ 7-prime} = 6 :: millennium [7R] [M10*]
  <- theory/breakthroughs/millennium-7-closure-2026-04-11.md
  "양면 Bernoulli 경계. ζ(2k) 분모 k=1..5 → n=6 분해. k=6 → 691 소수 침입. ζ(1-2k) 분자도 동일 대칭"
  signals: [SIG-7R-201]
  status: PROVEN (세션 기여, RH 자체는 미해결)

@MS RH-CORE-02 = ζ(2) = π²/n = π²/6 (Basel, Euler 1734) :: millennium [7R] [M10]
  "분모 = n = 6. B_2 = 1/n. ζ(2k) 공식 k=1. DFS26 재흡수"
  signals: [SIG-7R-001]

@MS RH-CORE-03 = ζ(6) = π⁶/945, argument 2k = n = 6 :: millennium [7R] [M10]
  "B_6 = 1/42 = 1/(n(n+1)). 945 = 3³·5·7"
  signals: [SIG-7R-002]

@MS RH-CORE-04 = SLE₆ 국소성: κ = n = 6 유일 (Lawler-Schramm-Werner 2001) :: millennium [7R] [M10]
  "fractal dim = 7/4 = (σ-sopfr)/τ. conformal invariance + locality 동시 만족 유일값"
  signals: [SIG-7R-208]

@MS RH-CORE-05 = Kim-Sarnak θ = 7/64 = (σ-sopfr)/(σ-τ)² :: millennium [7R] [M9]
  "GL(2) Maass 형식 eigenvalue 상한. Kim 2003 J.AMS"
  signals: [SIG-7R-203]

@MS RH-CORE-06 = RH 3중 공명: SLE₆ + Kim-Sarnak + Basel :: millennium [7R] [M7!]
  "세 분모 곱 = 4·64·6 = 1536 = σ·2^(σ-sopfr) = σ·2^β₀_YM → RH-YM 메가노드"
  signals: [SIG-7R-401]
  cross: [SIG-7Y-401]

@MS RH-OBS-01 = ζ 특수값 triple {ζ(-1),ζ(0),ζ(2)} = {-1/σ,-1/φ,π²/n} :: millennium [7R] [M10]
  signals: [SIG-7R-202]

@MS RH-OBS-02 = 처음 세 자명 영점 {-2,-4,-6} = {-φ,-τ,-n} :: millennium [7R] [M10]
  signals: [SIG-7R-201]

@MS RH-OBS-03 = Arakelov 1/σ 5중 독립 출현 CP¹ 메가노드 :: millennium [7R] [M10]
  signals: [SIG-7R-204]

@MS RH-OBS-04 = sqrt(6) 연분수 주기 = {φ,τ} = {2,4} 합=n :: millennium [7R] [M9]
  signals: [SIG-7R-206]

@MS RH-OBS-05 = Lévy-GCF 엔트로피 이중 상수 h/β = σ/n = φ :: millennium [7R] [M9]
  signals: [SIG-7R-205]

@MS RH-OBS-06 = Dyson 3=n/φ ensemble β ∈ {1,φ,τ} :: millennium [7R] [M9]
  signals: [SIG-7R-210]

@MS RH-OBS-07 = ζ(-9) = -1/132 = -1/(σ·(n+sopfr)) :: millennium [7R] [M9]
  signals: [SIG-7R-209]

@MS RH-OBS-08 = Selberg class GL_d 경계 d≤σ=12 + Kim-Sarnak θ=7/64 :: millennium [7R] [M9]
  signals: [SIG-7R-501]

@MS RH-OBS-09 = ζ(2k) 분모 시퀀스 {6,90,945,...} n 고유 첫항 :: millennium [7R] [M7]
  signals: [SIG-7R-502]

@MS RH-OBS-10 = Guth-Maynard 2024 sixth moment 기법 :: millennium [7R] [M7]
  signals: [SIG-7R-207]

@MS RH-OBS-11 = Riemann-Siegel Gabcke 전개 6차 정확도 표준 :: millennium [7R] [M7]
